Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, today we've brought together all you top honor students from the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys think it's totally unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you all have promising futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we know before we even try that we'll never amount to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing compared to the Sibyl System's cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyl's Judgment has robbed us of any chance we had for a good career.{#firstworldproblems}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We live with no hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you've all enjoyed Sibyl's blessing, you wouldn't understand, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw you take one of those helmets off earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So after causing all that mayhem, you thought you could just take the helmet off and play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's screwed up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really think I did all that, why don't you check my Hu—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You helmet-wearing bastards are raising the Area Stress level of the whole neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, just leave us the hell out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't raise our Crime Coefficients, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I read on the 'net before that if you fight in self-defense or attack criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually reduces your Crime Coefficient instead.
